cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with the task of emotion recognition from facial landmarks, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of deep learning algorithms, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of humanoid robots, which is related to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper deals with benchmark datasets, which is related to cs.MM (Multimedia).
